David Guetta - Listen (Album)(Deluxe Edition) 2014 

          Electro, French house, Hip House, Techno | Parlophone France

               320 kbps | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 01:04:24 | 149 Mb



David Guetta is set to release his new album 'Listen,' a new collection featuring a wealth of exclusive new material and an eclectic array of collaborators! 'Listen' will undoubtedly build on the remarkable success of his 2011 platinum selling album 'Nothing But The Beat,' which reached #3 on the ARIA Album chart and #1 on the ARIA Dance Album chart. It also earned Guetta multiple awards including a Grammy, AMA and was widely credited as changing the landscape for electronic music world-wide. Following on from chart topping track "Lovers On The Sun," David Guetta is about to shift the needle yet again with his new global lead single "Dangerous," featuring once more the vocal talents of emergent new artist Sam Martin.
